<p><strong>Founded:</strong> 29 September 1998</p>
<p><strong>Location:</strong> Mare Imbrium, Lunar surface.</p>
<p><strong>Site Function:</strong> Research, Specialised Containment, Remote Observation</p>
<p><strong>Size:</strong> Area of 12.4km<sup>2</sup></p>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
