<li>Assistant Site Director (<span style="color: #b30000">Yerkov Kal</span>) resigned from position, citing the position was unnecessary and hazardous under the context of Lunar Area-32’s location.</li>
<li>Senior Researcher (<span style="color: #b30000">Daniel Thorn</span>) assigned as Assistant Director of Personnel.</li>
<li>Lunar Area-32 and Site Director (<span style="color: #b30000">Cyrus Hourdoon</span>) noted for <span style="text-decoration: underline;">moderate priority monitoring</span>.</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
