<li>Assistant Director of Research (<span style="color: #b30000">Daniel Schröder</span>) reassigned off-site by Site Director (<span style="color: #b30000">Cyrus Hourdoon</span>), citing a lack of progress at Lunar Area-32.</li>
<li>Junior Researcher (<span style="color: #b30000">Dillan Polsun</span>) assigned as Assistant Director of Research.</li>
</ul>
<p><span style="white-space: pre-wrap;">&#32;</span><br />
